oise equivalent power\nis in the observational relevant $10^{-17}~W/\\sqrt{Hz}$ range. The device, as\nexpected from 3-D simulations, is polarisation-sensitive, paving the way to\nspectro-polarimetry measurements over very large instantaneous field-of-views.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Nov 2022 11:27:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Nov 2022 12:58:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-16"}
