 composing transformations or minimises accumulated\nerror may no longer be required. The implementation code and volunteer data\nwill be made publicly available ensuring reproducibility and further research.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Nov 2022 13:18:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 4 Feb 2023 17:08:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-07"}
